						spanning companies like T-Systems, Immobilien Scout 24, and Deutsche Post E-Post Development,
						where I helped transform monolithic systems into modern microservices platforms.
					</p>
					<p class="mb-4">
						Throughout my career, I've focused on Continuous Integration, Continuous Delivery, DevOps,
						and Agile Software Development. I believe in a cooperative management style built on open
						and honest communication, helping teams deliver customer value through modern software
						engineering and product development practices.
					</p>
					<p>
						Beyond my professional work, I share my knowledge and experience as a lecturer,
						supporting the next generation of software engineers in higher education.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

